<br>
Just to clear this up...the legs, arms, and helmet last 18 minutes.  <br>
<br>
The gloves (strength) and boots (dex, but good luck getting some) last about an hour, once you get up there in level.  The glove effect also stacks with most strength buffs other than Focus types and Dance of the Blade.  So with the cobalt boots effect, it's +55 strength.  With a shaman non-focus/HoS str buff, it's a bit more.  The boots stack with pretty much every dex buff besides Boon of the Garou.<br>
<br>
